        "description": "Testing performed per ASTM F1717-21 static compression-bending protocol at a single displacement rate (5 mm/min) and ambient temperature (23±2°C). Gradation 2 achieved: test conditions documented and controlled; however, only a single test condition (rate, temperature) was evaluated, preventing Gradation 3 which requires multi-condition coverage."
      },
